HEADWORD: Methanometer
<hw>Meth`a*nom"e*ter</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Methane</ets> + <ets>-meter</ets>.]</ety> <def>An instrument,
resembling a eudiometer, to detect the presence and amount of methane,
as in coal mines.</def>⟦br⟧
